Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:39.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}回過神來就一直在你身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:47.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}比任何人都煩惱得多 失落得多 哭得多 笑得多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}逐漸在加速著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:57.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}跨越天空 向你傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:02.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}緊緊地懷抱著那明確的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:08.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}那一定如同心中那剛萌芽的堅強
